These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
The people have 5 different jobs:  engineer, mechanic, teacher, accountant, photographer
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
House: modern, victorian, colonial, tower, cottage
 1. the cottage house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 2. the teacher is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the photographer is on the left of the modern house##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the modern house is the engineer##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the tower house##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the colonial house##1
11. the person drinking tea is between the chinese and the photographer##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the mechanic##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | almond-milk | tea     | coffee   | lemonade |
| Job   | teacher     | mechanic      | accountant | photographer   | engineer    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| House           | victorian | colonial      | cottage     | tower   | modern     |

