.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
House: gothic-revival, art-deco, futuristic, colonial, palace
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, daisy, amaryllis, marigold
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, metal, pop, reggae
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, rowing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the palace house is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is in the middle##1
 5. the palace house is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the art-deco house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who growsamaryllis##1
11. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the colonial house is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who growsmarigold and the futuristic house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| House         | gothic-revival | palace     | futuristic   | art-deco   | colonial |
| Flower   | marigold  | zinnia | poppy | amaryllis | daisy        |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | gospel      | pop       | reggae       | ambient       |
| Sport         | basketball | volleyball  | tennis    | badminton    | rowing        |

