.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, onion, papaya, tomato, watermelon
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, june, december, february, august
There are 5 different favourite colors: amber, pink, aquamarine, brown, blood-red
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the pakistani is between the person who likes brown and the person eating tomato##2
 5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes pink##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes brown is the british##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
12. the british is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
13. the person who likes pink is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | watermelon  | papaya     | tomato   | onion     | artichoke |
| Birthday         | august | january    | december  | february | june   |
| Color   | pink        | amber    | blood-red     | aquamarine     | brown    |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | indonesian | japanese | pakistani | british   |

