The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, lawyer, manager, social-worker, writer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, skateboarding, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the fan of house is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the fan of blues is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the fan of trance is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 9. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
10. the fan of punk is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | house       | reggae   | blues      | punk    |
| Birthday       | november | december        | october       | february       | september |
| Job        | writer     | lawyer        | social-worker | dancer        | manager  |
| Sport      | volleyball | skateboarding | climbing      | weightlifting | parkour  |

