There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, australian, french, polish, turkish
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, rowing, skiing, volleyball
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 3. the ranch-style house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 4. the tower house is on the right of the french##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the ranch-style house is between the owner of the rabbit and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the snake is on the right of the french##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the rabbit and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the futuristic house is on the right of the polish##1
13. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| House      | colonial  | ranch-style      | tower   | futuristic   | gothic-revival   |
| Pet   | rabbit    | goldfish   | snake   | horse | lizard     |
| Nationality   | argentine | french     | polish   | turkish | australian |
| Sport         | badminton | volleyball | baseball | rowing  | skiing     |

