 2. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 8. the person watching epic movies is the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the fan of r&b is between the person watching epic movies and the ritmeester-smoker##2
12. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
13. the alhambra-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |    5    |
