.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There are 5 different nationalities: mexican, german, canadian, indian, australian
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, satire, comedy, fantasy
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball, sailing
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, train, trike, van
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the german is the person watching comedy movies##1
 4. the mexican is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the german##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the person who's sport is golf and the person watching satire movies##2
12. the indian is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the canadian is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Nationality    | canadian       | indian    | australian | german  | mexican        |
| Movie-Genre       | fantasy | animation | satire  | comedy | documentary    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Transport   | trike       | train      | van      | motorbike | quad-bike  |

