.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, russian, mexican, indian, pakistani
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ebony, azure, amber, lavender
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, hip-hop, house, trance
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 2. the indian is between the person who likes azure and the mexican##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the indian##1
 4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the pakistani and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the pakistani##1
10. the argentine is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
11. the mexican is the person who likes ebony##1
12. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Nationality           | russian | mexican | indian | pakistani    | argentine  |
| Color   | amber  | ebony    | fuchsia | azure    | lavender |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | blues        | ambient   | house    | trance     |

