.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: turquised-games, chess, photography, puzzles, skydiving
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, davidoff, fonseca, montecristo, baccarat
5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, turquise, emerald, lilac, amber
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 2. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the vegafina-smoker and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who likes black and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is turquised-games##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's hobby is turquised-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is turquised-games is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | photography | puzzles   | chess      | turquised-games |
| Cigar   | vegafina   | montecristo    | davidoff | baccarat | fonseca      |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goldfish    | cat       | lizard     | mouse      |
| Color     | emerald | amber        | black  | turquise        | lilac    |

