.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, reading, lily-climbing, skydiving
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, rose, amaryllis, sunflower, lily
City: nizza, rome, edinburgh, liverpool, prague
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person who growslily##2
 3. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the person who growsazalea##1
 5. the person who growsazalea is between the person traveling to prague and the person who growsamaryllis##2
 6. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the person who's hobby is lily-climbing is the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is the person who growsrose##1
10. the person who's hobby is lily-climbing is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking  | cooking      | lily-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| Flower   | amaryllis | azalea    | lily    | sunflower       | rose         |
| City   | liverpool  | rome | prague    | edinburgh     | nizza      |

 